<paragraph base="F7282970" principles="no" id="IFRS01_D6"><paranum>D6</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="D6"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS01_P0525">A <xref base="F7282733" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0231">first&#x2011;time adopter<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0135"/></ph></xref> may elect to use a <xref base="F7282736" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0239">previous GAAP<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0299"/></ph></xref> revaluation of an item of property, plant and equipment at, or before, the <xref base="F7282728" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0223">date of transition to IFRSs<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0071"/></ph></xref> as <xref base="F7282729" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0224">deemed cost<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0074"/></ph></xref> at the date of the revaluation, if the revaluation was, at the date of the revaluation, broadly comparable to:</p><ol base="F7282972" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS01_L0047"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F7282973" id="IFRS01_P0526"><xref base="F7282730" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_DI0003" scope="local">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref>; or</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F7282975" id="IFRS01_P0527">cost or depreciated cost in accordance with <xref base="F7282734" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0232">IFRSs<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0199"/></ph></xref>, adjusted to reflect, for example, changes in a general or specific price index.</p>                </li></ol></body></paragraph>